Title: Alcon O2 Optix Monthly Contact Lens(-4.75, Clear, Pack of 6)
Description: Don’t let your near-sighted vision hamper your comfort and safety while you indulge in some adventurous water sports. Get splatter-free and crystal-clear vision while scuba diving, skiing, or snorkelling by wearing these O2 Optix corrective power lenses from Alcon. Material and Design These Silicone-based lenses contain Lotrafilcon B that ensures optimum moisture retention for the good health of your eyes. It also promises maximum transmission of oxygen for healthy-looking eyes. Other Benefits The dirt- and deposit-resistant surfaces of these lenses ensure clear and unobstructed view for a month, even when worn daily.

Title: Alcon O2 Optix Monthly Contact Lens(-4.25, Clear, Pack of 6)
Description: Why should your myopic vision be a concern when you deck up for your sister’s wedding. Wear these Alcon O2 Optix lenses throughout the ceremonies and show off your eye make-up that would otherwise be hidden by spectacle frames. Lens Material Experience enhanced comfort and healthier eyes with these deposit-resistant silicone hydrogel lenses. These soft lenses are also designed to reduce dryness by transmitting about 98% oxygen to your eyes, and they resist accumulation of deposit on their surfaces. Pack of 6 Having this pack of monthly disposable lenses in your vanity case ensures you always have a spare one on hand.

Title: CooperVision Proclear Monthly Contact Lens(-9.5, Plano Clear, Pack of 6)
Alcon O2 Optix Monthly Contact Lens(-5.5, Clear, Pack of 6)
Description: Wearing spectacles may be the easiest way to cure a myopic vision, but it certainly isn’t very appealing. Say hello to medical advancements, and start wearing these O2 Optix contact lenses from Alcon for comfortable and consistently excellent vision. Material You will never feel irritation or dryness in your eyes, courtesy the Silicone-hydrogel base that also includes oxygen and Lotrafilcon B. Get crisp and clear vision, along with longer wearing comfort, with the deposit-resistant surfaces of these lenses. Combo Pack Keep this pack of 6 lenses in your drawer so you're covered for the next six months.

Title: Alcon O2 Optix Monthly Contact Lens(-5.25, Clear, Pack of 6)
Description: Have you stopped clicking selfies and posing for pictures with friends off-late only because you have started wearing spectacles? Well, equip your vanity case with this pack of 6 O2 Optix soft lenses from Alcon, and you will never have to hold yourself back from clicking pictures and posting them on your social-media profile. Premium Quality and Design The Silicone-hydrogel base includes oxygen and Lotrafilcon B in order to prevent dryness, redness or any other irritation in your eyes. You can wear these soft lenses all month long, thanks to their dirt- and deposit-resistant properties. Pack of 6 With this pack, you will always have a spare lens on hand in case of loss or damage.
